_sText:
Since my last map upload wasn't very good, I decided to create something new and better.

The following map is supposed to be a zombie one, but I still haven't finished everything so that's why it's in an alpha stage.
Please test and tell me what is good or bad and what I should change.

There are 2 CT and 2 T spawns. There's also kind of an advertisement in the swimming pool (CoreTemp); I've been allowed to put this as I asked from CoreTemp's creator.

There are a few secrets

I hope you'll like it.

PS: You must open the compressed folder with 7-Zip or any other software that handles .7z files.
